{"tid":2224184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲迪碧克冇得踢　經理人炮轟曼聯！","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T06:37:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"08ee2caeb76d45d457374c96cd5c9460fa079919","tid":2224184,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"曼聯今夏唯一矚目收購，就係用4,000萬鎊買荷蘭中場雲迪碧克，不過呢位23歲球星今季2場聯賽都淪為後備，第1場對水晶宮只係踢咗23分鐘，但已經射入球隊唯一入波，但上仗作客白禮頓，更要去到最後補時階段先至落場。雖然球季流流長，但雲迪碧克經理人已經忍唔住向曼聯發炮！<br />\n<br />\n雲迪碧克經理人史華特接受荷蘭媒體《Voetbal Primeur》訪問，講到雲迪碧克「入魔」情況嗰陣，好唔畀面咁炮轟曼聯：「做後備囉！我梗係唔滿意，落場踢幾分鐘可以做到咩？對白禮頓嘅絕殺12碼，雲迪碧克都有功勞，呢場波正常嚟講曼聯應該輸1比7！曼聯有個好強嘅陣容，呢啲比賽唔應該出現。<br />\n<br />\n智利球星阿歷斯山齊士早前自爆，當初加盟曼聯經過第1次練習後已經後悔，雲迪碧克又有冇覺得轉錯會呢？"},{"pid":"c61311f2cd7d08119a54de6cceb5757d8bb7cd46","tid":2224184,"uid":373567,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"獌有普巴同般費已經夠哂,獌只係當雲迪碧克係佢兩個後備,今年轉會冇人肯去獌得佢肯去就知獌咩料,今鑊雲迪碧克真係上左賊船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c366a4a925bc85547410294611c63d6b8f50ae3","tid":2224184,"uid":67248,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"呢場波正常嚟講曼聯應該輸1比7... 認同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d622cd063ea40a5c30c3eb0a0f38a6b2aaae5b","tid":2224184,"uid":61604,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似迪馬咁一季就走人<br />\n講真雲迪比去巴塞好過啦"},{"pid":"43e8d35d1b9716554650b16596051920bd44b4c7","tid":2224184,"uid":201601,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c61311f2cd7d08119a54de6cceb5757d8bb7cd46","tid":2224184,"uid":373567,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"獌有普巴同般費已經夠哂,獌只係當雲迪碧克係佢兩個後備,今年轉會冇人肯去獌得佢肯去就知獌咩料,今鑊雲迪碧克真係上左賊船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"普巴踢永昌官嗰場咁廢結果下一場繼續正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf076fa112743bb2e7cd5f87d94fa07530f4de52","tid":2224184,"uid":34858,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"踢得過一場波入一粒波就咁快覺得條友真係好撚fit carry到全隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蘇蛇邊有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122f56bbd00d5a2bfb21b8217998a2d1301d46cc","tid":2224184,"uid":57797,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"俾個垃圾教緊係廢啦，so 屎黑柴 球員時代 後備垃圾 做領隊 又係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340fb49c23cc97ab7d9ddd32fbd41b94fbb26440","tid":2224184,"uid":20473,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"獌狗需要啲識衝入禁區跌低底者識省人隻手既球員"},{"pid":"72685cd12ed4a7830decaf1357a95a676e65bc92","tid":2224184,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122f56bbd00d5a2bfb21b8217998a2d1301d46cc","tid":2224184,"uid":57797,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"俾個垃圾教緊係廢啦，so 屎黑柴 球員時代 後備垃圾 做領隊 又係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2134b27e6fb0b5399a83da3c6174b3bc26854537","tid":2224184,"uid":37528,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，蘇斯克查都on撚9，做領隊乜柒management, leadership都無，你咪撚話你係費sir教出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2cdfb10cb77626f0b47dd1ad20ac6150aa484f","tid":2224184,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep